## üîß Installation

### VS Code Extension
1. Open VS Code
2. Go to Extensions (Ctrl+Shift+X)
3. Search for "CroweLang"
4. Install the extension

### Compiler
```bash
# Via npm
npm install -g crowelang

# Via pip (Python target)
pip install crowelang

# From source
git clone https://github.com/croweai/crowelang.git
cd crowelang
npm install
npm run build
```

